snippet.title: Xterium: War Of Alliances -  new space strategy
snippet.description:
Xterium - a new space strategy now on your mobile phone in Google Play and App Store. Populate different types of planets, open and pump dozens of fleets. Create various upgrades and study anomalies. Explore and conquer free depths of space with Xterium

Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xterium.xteriummobail
Apple Store - https://apps.apple.com/us/app/xterium/id1658549646
